Augustine Chouchou Ngo Mback Batoum (onye amụrụ n'ụbọchị mbụ n'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 1997) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agbachitere dị ka ọnọ n'etiti nke aka ekpe nye otu egwuregwu Louves Miniproff na ndị otu egwuregwu ụmụ nwanyị Cameroon.
Ngo Mback agbaala Louves Miniproff na Cameroon bọọlụ.
Ngo Mback gbaara otu egwuregwu mba  Camerooon na ọkwa dị elu n'oge 2016 Africa Women Cup of Nations na nke 2020 CAF Women's Olympic Qualifying Tournament.
